com.metreeca.rest.handlers

Class Worker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Worker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler

    public final class Worker
extends Object
implements Handler
    Method-based request worker.

    Delegates request processing to a handler selected on the basis of the request HTTP method.

    Provides default user-overridable handling of OPTIONS and HEAD methods.
